51:49.473 --> 51:54.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She went to the supermarket to
buy food because
she is anticipating a lot of
guests.

51:54.678 --> 51:56.180 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Oh.

51:56.213 --> 52:00.017 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: So, that tells
you a little
something about her and them.

52:00.050 --> 52:03.787 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They were an inseparable and
wonderful pair.

52:03.821 --> 52:07.992 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And he -- you know, talk about a
life well-lived.

52:08.025 --> 52:08.959 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What more can you say?

52:08.993 --> 52:10.094 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Where did he go wrong?

52:10.127 --> 52:11.795 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I can't think of it.

52:11.829 --> 52:16.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
Miles O'Brien,
thanks so much for joining us
